I"m<h2 id="solution">Solution:</h2>

<p>Assuming $n = m^k$ for some $k \geq 1$, we have</p>

\[\begin{align*}
        S(n) &amp;\leq cm\log_2(m)S\left(\frac{n}{m}\right) + O(n)\\\\
        &amp;\leq cm\log_2(m)\left[cm\log_2(m)S\left(\frac{n}{m^2}\right) + O\left(\frac{n}{m}\right)  \right] + O(n) \\\\
        &amp;\leq cm\log_2(m)\left[cm\log_2(m)\left[cm\log_2(m) + S\left(\frac{n}{m^3}\right) + O\left(\frac{n}{m^2}\right) \right] + O\left(\frac{n}{m}\right) \right] + O(n) \\\\
        &amp;\vdots \\\\
        &amp;\leq (cm\log_2(m))^kS(1) + (cm\log_2(m))^{k - 1}O\left(\frac{n}{m^{k - 1}}\right) + (cm\log_2(m))^{k - 2}O\left(\frac{n}{m^{k - 2}}\right) + \cdots + (cm\log_2(m))O\left(\frac{n}{m}\right) + O(n) \\\\
        &amp;\leq \leq (cm\log_2(m))^kS(1) + (c\log_2(m))^{k - 1}O\left(\frac{n}{m^{k - 1}}\right) + (cm\log_2(m))^{k - 2}O\left(\frac{n}{m^{k - 2}}\right) + \cdots + (cm\log_2(m))O\left(\frac{n}{m}\right) + O(n)
        &amp;\leq (cm\log_2(m))^kS(2) + O(mn)\left[\sum_{i = 0}^{k - 1} (cm\log_2(m))^i\right] \\\\
        &amp;= (cm\log_2(m))^k + O(mn)\left[\frac{(cm\log_2(m))^k - 1}{cm\log_2(m) - 1} \right] \\\\
        &amp;= O((cm\log_2(m))^k) + O(mn) \cdot O((cm\log_2(m))^{k - 1}) \\\\
        &amp;= O((cm\log_2(m))^k) + O(mn(cm\log_2(m))^{k - 1}) \text{ (by lemma $3.2$)} \\\\
        &amp;= O((cm\log_2(m))^{k - 1}[cm\log_2(m) + mn]) \text{ (by lemma $3.2$)} \\\\
        &amp;= O\left((cm\log_2(m))^{\log_m(n) - 1}[cm\log_2(m) + mn] \right) \\\\
        &amp;= O\left(\frac{(cm\log_2(m))^{\log_m(n)}[cm\log_2(m) + mn]}{cm\log_2(m)} \right) \\\\
        &amp;= O\left(\frac{c^{\log_m(n)}(n)(\log_2(m))^{\log_m(n)})[cm\log_2(m) + mn]}{cm\log_2(m)} \right) \\\\
        &amp;= O\left(\frac{n^{\log_m(c)}(n)(n^{\log_m(\log_2(m))})[cm\log_2(m) + mn]}{cm\log_2(m)} \right) \\\\
        &amp;= O\left(n^{\log_m(c) + [\log_m(\log_2(m))] + 2} \right)
    \end{align*}\]

\[\qed\]
